    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Make a melee attack against all creatures in the area, which will deal half damage and knock back targets hit for 1d3 x 5 ft. Targets hit are also knocked @Condition[prone]{prone} (Fortitude negates). You may use this technique against inanimate, unattended objects of Medium-size or smaller.</p>\n\n\n\n",
